AB  - We analyse the influence of foreign exchange constraints on output growth in the LDCs by studying the effect that these constraints have on the speed of adjustment of both investment and import activities. We model the speed of adjustment of investment as a function of available foreign exchange resources and allow for imperfect substitutability between the domestic and the foreign capital stocks.
